data.description: Charming ground floor condo in Condominiums At City Horizon! Upon entering, you'll immediately notice the fresh paint that brightens up every corner of this home. The main living areas are adorned with beautiful hardwood flooring, creating an inviting and warm atmosphere, while plush new carpeting in the bedrooms adds a touch of luxury. The recently remodeled kitchen features new stainless steel appliances and elegant quartz countertops complemented by a stylish subway tile backsplash. The open concept design seamlessly connects the kitchen to the living room, where a cozy gas fireplace beckons you to unwind and relax. Natural light from the covered patio pours in, creating a warm welcoming ambiance. The primary suite offers a generous walk-in closet and an additional storage closet with shelving. The ensuite bathroom boasts dual sinks and a large soaking tub, providing the perfect escape for relaxation. Both bathrooms have been tastefully upgraded with new mirrors and hardware. Convenience is at your fingertips with an in-unit laundry room complete with extra storage space. Enjoy easy access to highways, parks, and much more. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful condo your new home!
